6","article":"George, if you have time you should check out the cartoon Avengers: Earths Mightiest Heros which ran on Disney XD for two seasons a couple of years ago (it's on Netflix). They do a really nice job of bringing the characters to life and staying true to the comics. Unfortunately, the series was canceled and replaced with a series that is more true to the movies than the comics.<br /><br />Agree with you on Hawkeye, initially I thought Jeremy Renner was good casting but when I saw the movie it didn't turn out so well (the cartoon I mentioned does a good job with Hawkeye). Also agree on Hank Pym, he could've been used in place of the Stellan Skarsgard character in the first movie and then brought along in the second movie. Now the new Ant-man movie sounds like a disaster as they're skipping straight to the second Ant-man. ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 12 2014, 02:15:51 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Avengers","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/OberynMattell","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"OberynMattell","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2738803","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=72071300&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"OberynMattell","ctime_ts":1413080151,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/124105880/72558992","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19628770#t19628770","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19628770#t19628770","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19628770#t19628770","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2815592","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/mahveshm","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19628770,"talkid":76674,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19628770#t19628770","upictitle":"Mahvesh Murad: pic#124105880","article":"Hello!<br /><br />Thanks so much for posting the show here. Appreciate you taking the time out to do the interview. Hope you're well. <br /><br />Mahvesh ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 12 2014, 03:37:02 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Thank you!","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/mahveshm","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"mahveshm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2815592","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=72558992&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"mahveshm","ctime_ts":1413085022,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/109915172/10560429","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629026#t19629026","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629026#t19629026","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629026#t19629026","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"nycfalcon","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://nycfalcon.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19629026,"talkid":76675,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629026#t19629026","upictitle":"nycfalcon: pic#109915172","article":"I absolutely appreciate these. Thanks. I was especially keen on what Robin said about her figuring out the untaught process of being a professional writer. Artists almost never mention that. It's a small but most critical detail for people who want to do that for a living.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 12 2014, 04:40:36 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://nycfalcon.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"nycfalcon","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"nycfalcon","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://nycfalcon.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"nycfalcon","ctime_ts":1413088836,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/121411156/65344279","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629282#t19629282","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629282#t19629282","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629282#t19629282","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2058420","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/GeekFurious","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19629282,"talkid":76676,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629282#t19629282","upictitle":"GeekFurious: pic#121411156","article":"The Jane Johnson and Robin Hobb panel was very encouraging. There are times when I wonder why I'm spending so much time writing a story that likely no one will ever read... but I can't help but write it.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 12 2014, 11:23:17 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Thank you","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/GeekFurious","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"GeekFurious","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2058420","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=65344279&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"GeekFurious","ctime_ts":1413112997,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/15363718/1873","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629538#t19629538","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629538#t19629538","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629538#t19629538","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"segue","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://segue.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19629538,"talkid":76677,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629538#t19629538","upictitle":"segue: me?","article":"<p dir=\"ltr\">Nice little interview, thanks for sharing.<br>Purity is not a bad thing. Agree about slabbing; pretty much like locking away memories, and throwing away the key!</p>","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 12 2014, 17:03:05 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://segue.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"segue","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"segue","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://segue.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"segue","ctime_ts":1413133385,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/64164284/12356116","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629794#t19629794","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629794#t19629794","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629794#t19629794","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"mariefoxprice","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://mariefoxprice.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19629794,"talkid":76678,"etime_ts":"1413159022","thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19629794#t19629794","upictitle":"mariefoxprice: pic#64164284","article":"I've been listening to these tonight.  I love the discussion of naming conventions.  <br /><br />A few years ago I encountered a creative writing lecturer who believed \"Never give 2 characters names starting with the same letter.\"  Funnily enough, both myself and another member of the class- also a fan of yours! - had done it and we'd both used brothers!  <br /><br />In my case the names were carefully chosen to reflect the world I was writing in, and had very specific connotations that the lecturer clearly didn't understand, so I was annoyed that the issue had even been raised.  I'd been a fan of ASOIAF for almost 14 years at that point so I found the idea of confusing readers with the names of 2 characters rather bizarre!  Worse, the lecturer had never even heard of ASOIAF or Game of Thrones (a major heresy in my mind!)<br /><br />I changed one of the names to please her but it didn't feel right at all.   I'm definitely going to change it back when I have the time and inclination to work on that particular story again!  If I am in a position to publish that story and a reader complains about the names, I'll just point out all the many Brandon Starks and all the other wonderful name variations you have.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 13 2014, 00:07:45 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://mariefoxprice.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"mariefoxprice","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"mariefoxprice","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://mariefoxprice.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"etime":"October 13 2014, 00:10:22 UTC","dname":"mariefoxprice","ctime_ts":1413158865,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/123436130/65320653","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19630050#t19630050","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19630050#t19630050","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19630050#t19630050","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"jcp24","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://jcp24.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19630050,"talkid":76679,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19630050#t19630050","upictitle":"jcp24: pic#123436130","article":"Hello George,<br /><br />Thanks for the great links.  I have really enjoyed listening to all of your diverse experiences and inspirations.  I especially enjoyed this last interview you posted from the 89 Chapters with the musical inspirations.  Great stuff!  Several times during the interviews, you mention fanzines.  Are there any current fanzines that you follow or recommend that have kept your interest?","siteroot":"http: