ttp://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1413822752,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/123320640/70685480","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19631586#t19631586","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19631586#t19631586","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19631586#t19631586","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2573139","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/clonedllama","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19631586,"talkid":76685,"etime_ts":"1413773471","thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19631586#t19631586","upictitle":"Caaaarl: pic#123320640","article":"When it comes to the South Park episode, I think Matt and Trey had definitely seen the show. There's been some criticism from some people that the show favors female nudity over male nudity. There may or may not be some merit to that argument.<br /><br />So I think they intentionally went in the exact opposite direction as a reference to that, especially since one of the characters becomes obsessed with that over everything else the show has to offer. I think Cartman says something like, \"You're focusing on the wrong stuff!\" (in a much funnier manner of course). At least that's my take on it. Knowing Matt and Trey, they may have just thought it was funny that their version of you is obsessed with wieners! It's hard to know for sure. The line between brilliance and being completely juvenile is often rather murky with them. ;)<br /><br />Lots of great interviews. I'll have to check out the big one you did with Robin Hobb later this week. I love her books!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 20 2014, 02:49:51 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/clonedllama","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"clonedllama","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2573139","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=70685480&t=I","alias":0}],"etime":"October 20 2014, 02:51:11 UTC","dname":"clonedllama","ctime_ts":1413773391,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/123931444/72125338","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19639522#t19639522","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19639522#t19639522","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19639522#t19639522","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2748239","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://www.facebook.com/vera.deferran","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19639522,"talkid":76716,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/385506.html?thread=19639522#t19639522","upictitle":"Vera de Ferran: pic#123931444","article":"Do you consider doing here a Q&A section with the blog readers questions? ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"October 21 2014, 18:12:32 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"https://www.facebook.com/vera.de